{"tid":757835,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【重回那些年】離樂壇15年 男子組合SKY四缺一重組","createTime":"2018-07-27T07:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T12:53:28.000Z","uid":27064,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"57739dbc45bf7b86f8f64a936cfe566ec567f4ef","tid":757835,"uid":27064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T07:09:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180727/large/1532673313_0a0c.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180727%2Flarge%2F1532673313_0a0c.jpg&d=rHN6vsleqB0umXlyQsQjUrZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=ff78c863\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180727/large/1532673313_0a0c.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n80後嘅你，仲記唔記得樂壇曾經有過一隊男子組合叫SKY？唔記得都唔出奇，事關佢哋由出道到消失只有短短2年時間。不過，最近SKY原來靜悄悄搞重組，雖然當年隊長潘卓楠（Gilbert）未有加入，但其餘四位成員，包括以前英文名叫Yani嘅嚴嘉駿（Moses）、林卓健（Kin）、趙耀邦（Bong）及梁俊邦（Bonald）都齊晒人，今日重有新歌《趁今天有空》推出添！<br />\n<br />\n當年全部只有10幾、20歲嘅成員，今日都已經年過30成為中佬喇，曾經同傅珮嘉發展姐弟戀嘅Bonald，今年3月都已經成家立室。問他們為何有重組這念頭？SKY接受《蘋果》訪問話：「其實我哋都有13年冇約過，就係喺Bonald婚禮再見面，仲一齊上台合唱，前經理人喺facebook live睇到，就約我哋傾紀念project。」<br />\n講到過去15年大家做過啲乜？Bonald原來一直做健身教練，Kin就做過主持，至於Bong係跳舞老師，而Moses就去咗做地產經紀。佢哋話今次唔可以五位一體的當有啲可惜，但Gilbert想專心教小朋友游水，大家都會尊重。<br />\n有指現在樂壇比以前更難生存，問他們有什麼期望？SKY話現在香港樂壇跳唱組合比較少，佢哋最希望可以百花齊放。講到當年短短兩年就解散，佢哋承認嗰啲因為發展麻麻，係時候諗將來，15年後合體就有唔同想法，依家可以放心去追夢，最多辛苦啲。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180727/58492843\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180727%2F58492843&d=rHN6vsleqB0umXlyQsQjUrZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=d8255c38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180727%2F58492843&h=dd5a51c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180727/58492843</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇印象?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e75725718200ed72d74c85c6a97c19dc64a39e","tid":757835,"uid":27064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T07:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180727/large/1532673314_d1a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180727%2Flarge%2F1532673314_d1a1.jpg&h=6a9ce107&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180727/large/1532673316_43fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180727%2Flarge%2F1532673316_43fc.jpg&h=05e9c027&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180727/large/1532673318_9061.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180727%2Flarge%2F1532673318_9061.jpg&h=bafd8f5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180727/large/1532673321_538a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180727%2Flarge%2F1532673321_538a.jpg&h=3dc0a1fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3baaa2439b40cf0101af772f7182625a5b988fda","tid":757835,"uid":82917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T07:12:55.000Z","msg":"口袋情人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6591b01e578c0118c684825ab1f1ba4131efa4","tid":757835,"uid":34935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T07:13:44.000Z","msg":"三分區"},{"pid":"4e81db64b34e3a5a396ca5477c8f0624844f4b60","tid":7